Tavatron:

Tavatron rolled to the side, catching the blunt of Brightblade's attack in 
her left shoulder:

"You'll pay for that Predacon!" Tavatron rolls to her feet and swings her 
staff at BrightBlade's legs. Her shoulder screamed with pain and her fur was 
burned. She took a quick glance in Dinobot's direction. His face was 
bleeding again, but Scourge was walking around headless. One Pred down, so 
far so good. Out of the corner of her eye she saw some 'bots enter the ark:

*That is definitely not good.* Tavatron thought as she turned her attention 
back to BrightBlade.
